ths long. Neighboring boutiques sell everything from interestingly shaped cork handbags \u2026<\/p> \r\n\r\n\r\n","section":{"name":"U.S.","slug":"us","url":"http:\/\/time.com\/us\/","description":"The latest news and analysis on crime, religion, education, transportation, weather, immigration, sports, drugs, the law, and other news from around the nation"},"tag":{"name":"nation","slug":"nation","url":"http:\/\/time.com\/tag\/nation\/"},"tags":"Detroit|nation","hero":{"class":"wide","thumbnail":"http:\/\/timedotcom.files.wordpress.com\/2014\/11\/detroit_andrew_moore.jpg?w=100&h=100&crop=1","src":{"small":"http:\/\/timedotcom.files.wordpress.com\/2014\/11\/detroit_andrew_moore.jpg?w=280","small_2x":"http:\/\/timedotcom.files.wordpress.com\/2014\/11\/detroit_andrew_moore.jpg?w=560","large":"http:\/\/timedotcom.files.wordpress.com\/2014\/11\/detroit_andrew_moore.jpg?w=840","large_2x":"http:\/\/timedotcom.files.wordpress.com\/2014\/11\/detroit_andrew_moore.jpg?w=1680"},"credit":"Photograph by Andrew Moore","caption":"A group of diversity activists celebrate at a downtown\u00a0Detroit park ","alt":"","providers":[]},"id":3583133,"encoded_url":"http%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3583133%2Fdetroit-turns-up%2F","encoded_shortlink":"http%3A%2F%2Fwp.me%2Fp5HMd-f28t","encoded_title":"Detroit+Turns+Up","twitter_text":"Detroit%20Turns%20Up","twitter_via":"TIME","subjects":[null],"ads":{"neg":"false","post_title":"Detroit Turns Up"},"Partner_Module":{"partner":"Select","post_title":"Detroit Turns Up"},"email_title":"Detroit%20Turns%20Up%20%7C%20TIME","email_body":"Detroit%20Turns%20Up%0A%0AAn%20unlikely%20deal%20lifts%20Motown%20out%20of%20bankruptcy%20%0D%0A%0A%0Ahttp%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3583133%2Fdetroit-turns-up%2F","icon":"key","omniture":{"modules":"rr-mag|rr-share"},"outbrain":{"url":"http:\/\/time.com\/3583133\/detroit-turns-up\/","widget_id":"AR_6","hide":false}},{"url":"http:\/\/time.com\/3560726\/a-shadow-falls-on-china\/","shortlink":"http:\/\/wp.me\/p5HMd-eWj4","title":"A Shadow 